Rowdy Wolf:




"No, this is it." he said to KitKat. He turned his head, to where Zyber was. 
"I'm going to help my friend. You are welcomed to follow. But your decision 
is your own destiny." He turned his head back to KitKat and Terrorsaur. He 
put his rifle behind his armor and fur, then transformed to his beast mode. 
"Then we shall go?" he said to them. "Lead the way."

Terrorsaur lifted himself into the air and transformed to beast mode. He 
lowered down and grabbed the bundle of furs in his claws. He even managed to 
put a fur blanket over his back and wings.
